import React, { useRef, useEffect, useState } from "react"; import Contact from "./Contact"; import "./home.css"; import Project from "./Project"; function Home() { const img1Ref = useRef(null); const img2Ref = useRef(null); const img3Ref = useRef(null); const navbarRef = useRef(null); const [sticky, setSticky] = useState(""); useEffect(() => { const handleScroll = () => { let val = window.scrollY; if (val < 700) { img1Ref.current.style.top = val * 0.8 + "px"; img2Ref.current.style.top = val * 0.6 + "px"; } if (val > 500) setSticky("sticky"); else setSticky(""); console.log(val); }; window.addEventListener("scroll", handleScroll); return () => window.removeEventListener("scroll", handleScroll); }, []); return (
